videos.description: Desmond Bane gets the pass from Ja Morant and knocks down the open 3.

videos.headline: Ja sets up Bane for a 3

videos.description: Anthony Edwards rises up to reject Ja Morant's layup out of bounds with authority.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ant gets up for a block on Ja) 2022/04/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ant gets up for a block on Ja

videos.description: Karl-Anthony Towns sees no resistance as he gets inside for a monstrous one-handed slam.

videos.headline: KAT glides in for emphatic finish

videos.description: Patrick Beverley subtly rocks the baby after he fights through contact to get the tough and-1 to go down.

videos.headline: Pat Bev rocks the baby after this and-1 bucket

videos.description: Karl-Anthony Towns gets inside and goes through multiple defenders to get the and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KAT gets the tough and-1 to go down) 2022/04/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: KAT gets the tough and-1 to go down

videos.description: Ja Morant readjusts mid-air to get the nice and-1 bucket to go in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ja readjusts for smooth and-1 finish) 2022/04/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ja readjusts for smooth and-1 finish

videos.description: Jaden McDaniels throws down a dunk on the fast break and Alex Rodriguez leaps out of his seat to celebrate with other fans.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (A-Rod hyped after Wolves go on a run) 2022/04/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: A-Rod hyped after Wolves go on a run

videos.description: Anthony Edwards gets into the body of Jaren Jackson Jr. and manages to drop in a challenging and-1 layup.

videos.headline: Ant goes through Jackson for a tough and-1

videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin drops a dime to Jaden McDaniels for a big dunk in the face of Jaren Jackson Jr., then sets up Karl-Anthony Towns for another huge flush in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (McLaughlin sets his teammates up for 2 big slams) 2022/04/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: McLaughlin sets his teammates up for 2 big slams

videos.description: Tyus Jones gets the pass from Ja Morant and laces a huge 3-pointer to give the Grizzlies a 106-102 lead.
